Module main.model
Package main.controller

Class ModifyProductController

java.lang.Object
main.controller.ModifyProductController
All Implemented Interfaces:
javafx.fxml.Initializable
public class ModifyProductController extends Object implements javafx.fxml.Initializable
Product Modifier Controller. LOGICAL ERROR : Initially had some issues getting the parts to load for each individual product and be unique to those products. I fixed this by setting up an empty arraylist for the new products parts. As parts are added to the product in the application they are added to this "temp" part list. When saved, there is a loop that loops over the temp part list and adds those parts to the products real part list. FUTURE ENHANCEMENT: Only show the available parts that aren't already assigned to the product from "all parts" instead of just showing a static table of all parts. With that, you would need to implement a count for the part, since you could add more of one part.
